; NESTED AGGREGATES: A RECORD WITH AN ARRAY FIELD AND A RECORD FIELD, PLUS AN
; ARRAY OF RECORDS. ACCESS CHAINS FREELY: `B.CELLS I [`, `B.CORNER.X`, `PTS I [ .Y`.

!R POINT
    X W
    Y W

!R BOARD
    CELLS A 4 W
    CORNER POINT

!MAIN W
    !B BOARD
    !PTS A 2 POINT
    9 B.CELLS 2 [ !
    5 B.CORNER.X !
    7 PTS 0 [ .Y !
    B.CELLS 2 [  B.CORNER.X +  PTS 0 [ .Y +  PRINT   ; 9 + 5 + 7 = 21
